</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Photosensitive epilepsy</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:StarWarsPinballEpilepsyWarning.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/StarWarsPinballEpilepsyWarning.jpg/220px-StarWarsPinballEpilepsyWarning.jpg" width="220" height="165" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/StarWarsPinballEpilepsyWarning.jpg/330px-StarWarsPinballEpilepsyWarning.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/69/StarWarsPinballEpilepsyWarning.jpg/440px-StarWarsPinballEpilepsyWarning.jpg 2x" data-file-width="3264" data-file-height="2448" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:StarWarsPinballEpilepsyWarning.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>
Epilepsy warning label on a <a href="/wiki/Pinball_machine" title="Pinball machine" class="mw-redirect">pinball machine</a> with <a href="/wiki/Video" title="Video">video</a> components.</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><b>Photosensitive epilepsy</b> (<b>PSE</b>) is a form of <a href="/wiki/Epilepsy" title="Epilepsy">epilepsy</a> in which <a href="/wiki/Seizure" title="Seizure" class="mw-redirect">seizures</a> are <a href="/wiki/Seizure_trigger" title="Seizure trigger" class="mw-redirect">triggered</a> by visual stimuli that form patterns in time or space, such as flashing lights, bold, regular patterns, or regular moving patterns.</p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
<div id="toctitle">
