</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-4"><a href="#Fluorescent_lighting"><span class="tocnumber">1.2</span> <span class="toctext">Fluorescent lighting</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-5"><a href="#Video_games_and_Pinball_machines"><span class="tocnumber">1.3</span> <span class="toctext">Video games and Pinball machines</span></a></li>
